      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "DaVinci Resolve is a major offender — its text tools have limited or no RTL support even in the latest versions. Hebrew-speaking filmmakers routinely pre-reverse text before pasting it into Resolve titles and subtitles. Vegas Pro and many open-source editors (Shotcut, OpenShot) have the same problem." : {

    },
